Description
===========

This package is 2D PSV Hybrid code developed by Lianxing Wen
for calculating synthetic seismograms involving two dimensional
localized heterogeneous structures.

Reference
=========

Wen and Helmberger (1998), JGR

Requirement
===========

#. Seismic Analysis Code (SAC)

   You need SAC installed on your system, and
   $(SACHOME) set to the SAC installation directory.

#. Numerical Recipes (http://www.nr.com/)

   nrutil.h and nrutil.c from Numerical Recipes are needed, which should be purchased.

#. Generic Mapping Tools

   Some figures are plotted using GMT, it is not necessary.

Installation
============

Go to src directory, and run make.

Examples
========

Just change to the example diretory and run::

    perl RunModel.pl
